"""Test get_in_use_initiator."""
initiator = self.provisioning.get_in_use_initiator()
if initiator:
    self.assertIsInstance(initiator, str)
    self.assertIsNotNone(re.match(constants.INITIATOR_SEARCH_PATTERN,
        initiator))
else:
    self.skipTest(
        'test_get_available_initiator - Unable to get an in-use initiator.')
